1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:27,120
Then I might have to show you how
ruthless and insatiable Bandit Yai can be.

2
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,040
We're not going to sleep tonight, Pin.

3
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,880
Win, shoot his leg.

4
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,080
- Sorry, Manager. I must follow orders.
- Hey.

5
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,120
Get all the weapons ready.

6
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,000
<i>I will take Paisal Farm.</i>

7
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:39,200
All this vengeance will be settled today.

8
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,640
I will marry Pinanong.

9
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,920
- Huh?
- I'm willing to marry him.

10
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,200
Pin…

11
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:51,800
You're doing this because
you're planning something, aren't you?

12
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,560
Why do you think I'm planning something?

13
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,840
Because we don't love each other.

14
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,440
You don't love me,

15
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,880
but I love you.

16
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:29,440
Are you happy
messing with people's feelings?

17
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,720
You know my every move, huh?

18
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,120
Yeah.

19
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:46,280
You're just a pawn in my game.

20
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:53,520
Then please play around
with my life all you want.

21
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,520
Because all this time,

22
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:59,480
I haven't been important
in anyone's eyes anyway.

23
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,880
So you agreed to marry me

24
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,320
just to spite Tatsana, didn't you?

25
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,640
Feel free to use me for that.

26
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,040
Let's go.

27
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,320
Hey, you all can't gang up

28
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,680
on a law-abiding citizen like me.

29
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:39,280
Let go of me. Hey, let go.

30
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,280
I said let go.

31
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,080
Let go of me. Let go.

32
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,840
No one's doing anything to you.

33
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,080
Krong.

34
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,520
You don't have to worry.

35
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,040
That hitman died in a car accident.

36
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,600
Yai suspects us,
but there aren't any witnesses left.

37
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,920
What about Jerd and Kan?

38
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:05,920
I think they know things are looking bad,
so they're laying low.

39
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,040
I'll contact them.

40
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,800
Please don't be upset with me.

41
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,240
Let me help you relax tonight.

42
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,240
Relax?

43
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:23,240
Yai's going to marry Pin,

44
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:26,120
and half of the fortune
will fall into her hands.

45
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,760
So what would be left for us?

46
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:38,320
Huh? Pin's marrying Mr. Yai?

47
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,480
I'm confused.

48
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,800
Didn't Mr. Yai say
she stole the farm's money?

49
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,360
How did they end up together?

50
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,160
I don't know. It's the owner's business.

51
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,120
I'm just the messenger, okay?

52
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:54,400
Let's all help clean everything up
and tidy up all the plants and trees.

53
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,400
Alright?

54
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:58,560
And… is Jom still not back?

55
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:02,000
He called and said he was downtown
giving a statement all night.

56
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,160
But he'll be back soon.

57
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,160
Oh, there he comes.

58
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,480
Speak of the devil.

59
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,040
Well, how did it go, Jom?

60
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,920
The police are now suspecting that

61
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,120
the deceased hitman
might be from another area,

62
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,600
because they haven't found any evidence.

63
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,640
They'll probably proceed with DNA testing
and fingerprint identification

64
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,120
to search for criminal records.

65
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:27,240
I didn't want to give
too many details about the farm

66
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,280
since the owner
isn't exactly clean himself.

67
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,400
That's good.

68
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,720
The police shouldn't
be meddling with this farm.

69
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,480
And how's Pin, Dad?

70
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,960
Stop worrying about her.

71
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,360
From now on,
no one would dare pick on your Pin.

72
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,640
We can't just call her Pin now.

73
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,360
She's about to be the owner's wife,

74
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,280
so we should call her Madam Pin, right?

75
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,120
Pin's becoming the owner's wife?

76
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:09,240
I don't feel like I'm a slave at all.

77
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:12,720
I'm just happy
every time I can repay someone's kindness.

78
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,040
It's good to be grateful,

79
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,360
but you also need to know good from bad.

80
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:20,480
Most importantly, you should be able
to tell right from wrong.

81
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:30,360
Every time he fought with his dad,
he would come here.

82
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:34,160
This spot was where he let out his anger.

83
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:38,680
It was good that
he didn't take it out on others.

84
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,440
Mr. Yai misunderstood him.

85
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,840
Mr. Paisal loved him so much.

86
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,800
But he couldn't express it properly.

87
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,680
It's the same for Yai.

88
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,440
His words don't match his heart.

89
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:56,600
I think if this continues,

90
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,000
he will never be happy
until the day he dies.

91
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:04,480
I want to help him,

92
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,560
but I really don't know how to.

93
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,320
If you want to help someone,

94
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:13,320
you must first be strong and independent.

95
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,680
But I don't think

96
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,960
you're weak and puny

97
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,960
like Yai said you are, right?

98
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,400
Pin, come with us.

99
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,640
Where are we going, Jom?

100
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:38,120
I'll take you
somewhere far away from Mr. Yai.

101
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,200
I have relatives living
in another province.

102
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:43,159
Go hide there for a while,
and we'll figure out what to do.

103
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,880
I want to marry Mr. Yai.

104
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:51,440
Hey, are you out of your mind, Pin?

105
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:55,000
Did Yai force you to do this?

106
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,240
- I'll kill him.
- Don't do it, Jom.

107
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:01,440
Don't do anything to Mr. Yai,
or I'll hate you for the rest of my life.

108
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,720
Pin.

109
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,840
Thank you for your concern, Jin.

110
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,680
But this decision

111
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,600
was made with a sound mind.

112
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:15,040
And I'm willing to accept
any consequences that come.

113
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,360
Pin.

114
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:00,680
Thank you, Uncle Pload,
for doing what I asked.

115
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,080
All this vengeance

116
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,840
will be settled today.

117
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,520
Pinanong saved my life.

118
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,720
She shielded me from the bullets.

119
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,960
If she really hated me,

120
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:23,120
she wouldn't have
risked her life like that.

121
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,280
Pan.

122
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,520
Don't look at me, Dad.

123
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,680
I'm not a part of that.

124
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:36,160
Then I won't raid Paisal Farm,

125
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,560
and I won't hurt Pinanong.

126
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,080
But Mr. Yai,

127
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,240
you must meet with a lawyer

128
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,840
and declare to the police

129
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,280
that you're still alive.

130
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:53,000
That way, you can stand in court and
reclaim the rights to your inheritance,

131
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,960
as we have agreed.

132
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,240
Pan.

133
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,120
Call the lawyer.

134
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,200
Yes, Dad.

135
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,360
Let's go.

136
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,800
Mr. Yai!

137
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,640
Stop playing around like a child.

138
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,240
Only the law can help you.

139
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,040
I won't dare to stand in court.

140
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,840
I'm scared.

141
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:26,640
I'm scared to speak about my past
with that man in front of everyone.

142
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:31,360
I feel hurt every time
I'm reminded that Dad hated me.

143
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,680
I don't want
any of that inheritance, Uncle.

144
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,000
I just wanted to come home.

145
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:43,520
And the only one
making Paisal Farm feel like home…

146
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,440
is Pinanong.

147
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,440
I'll let you have your way.

148
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:05,520
But that doesn't mean I trust Pinanong

149
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,760
or forgive that Madam Krongsuk.

150
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,200
I've never forgiven her myself.

151
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:13,320
I'll make her show her true colors
so everyone can see.

152
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:15,440
By throwing your life into marriage?

153
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:20,320
Using all your hard-earned money

154
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,160
as a dowry for her subordinate?

155
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,760
I think it's a waste.

156
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,120
If I really become the legitimate heir,

157
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:30,440
the most I can do is kick her out.

158
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,760
But I won't have any evidence
to put her in prison.

159
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,680
What evidence, Mr. Yai?

160
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:45,840
I suspect that my dad might not have died
from illness, Uncle Pload.

161
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,280
‪Really?

162
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,440
Madam.

163
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,400
Madam. Please don't be afraid.

164
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:08,880
I'll never let Pin marry Mr. Yai.

165
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,160
It's clear, isn't it?

166
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:15,240
You want the farm owner as your in-law

167
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,640
more than you want to serve
an illegitimate wife like me.

168
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,080
That's not true, Madam.

169
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,760
That's not true at all.

170
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:24,560
Madam, I've never not cared about you.

171
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:26,120
I swear.

172
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:30,080
No need to pretend to be loyal.

173
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:34,040
I don't believe your tears
or your words anymore.

174
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,720
No…

175
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:39,760
Madam. Madam. Please believe me.

176
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,960
I would never think
of betraying you, Madam.

177
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,360
I can even give my life to you.

178
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:49,920
Then kill Yai for me.

179
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,240
Can you do that?

180
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:54,680
Go ahead. Prove that you love me. Go.

181
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,880
- Go ahead! Go!
- Mom! Madam!

182
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:03,960
Go ahead.

183
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:07,680
Slap me. But don't touch my mom.

184
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,400
Finally,

185
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,920
you've shown me your true colors.

186
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:17,000
Do it. Gang up on me.

187
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:19,560
You hold the upper hand now, right? Do it!

188
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,560
Pin.

189
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,120
Tell Madam right now

190
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:29,000
that you were violated
and forced by Yai to marry him.

191
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,120
Tell her!

192
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,720
Tell her now!

193
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,360
Mr. Yai didn't force me.

194
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,920
I'm willing.

195
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:41,200
I have to hand it to you, Pinanong.

196
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:44,920
It wasn't a waste to send you to school.

197
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,480
Please forgive me, Madam.

198
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:53,360
But I see this as the best way
to repay those who were kind to me.

199
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:57,880
Mr. Paisal, you, and Mr. Yai.

200
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:02,880
Hey.

201
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:07,880
My father took your parents in long
before you were born.

202
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:12,040
But you're saying
you want to repay Paisal and Yai?!

203
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:14,120
Your daughter is unbelievable.

204
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,160
Go.

205
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,160
Go have a good life
with your new master.

206
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,360
Go! I said get out!

207
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,520
- Go! Get out!
- Madam.

208
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,920
- Get out of my face! Go!
- Madam!

209
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,120
Get out!

210
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,760
Are you satisfied, you old bastard?

211
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,440
Your son is quite a pain.

212
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:46,600
I will never lose to you so easily.

213
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,440
I'll let you choose.

214
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,880
If you still want to marry Yai,

215
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,880
we'll cut ties as mother and daughter!

216
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,320
I can't choose.

217
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,240
I have to marry Mr. Yai,

218
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,760
and I'll never leave you.

219
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:06,360
You said you haven't slept with him.

220
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:09,160
Then why are you betraying
Madam for him still? Huh?

221
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,760
Mr. Yai is Mr. Paisal's son.

222
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:15,560
He took in Madam's family
and the two of us.

223
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:19,080
We owe Mr. Yai too,
since he paid for your medical bills.

224
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:20,520
Was I wrong, Mom?

225
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,560
That's stolen money!

226
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,160
Ever since he came back,

227
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:28,200
he has been bullying
and harming Madam and Mr. Na!

228
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,800
If you marry him,

229
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:33,160
that means you're joining him
in harming Madam.

230
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:36,920
So what if I promise that Mr. Yai
won't do anything to Madam ever again?

231
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:45,960
Fine!

232
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,120
Marry him then!

233
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:53,960
But go to the wedding with messed-up hair.

234
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,760
- Come here!
- Mom! Mom!

235
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:59,160
Mom, don't do this. Please don't.

236
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,200
Pin!

237
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,880
Mom, please.

238
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,080
Don't.

239
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:05,040
I'm doing this for everyone, really.

240
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,520
You have to believe me.

241
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:09,319
- Aunt Un. Aunt Un, enough.
- Pin.

242
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,520
Let go, Aunt Un.

243
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:14,400
- Stop. That's enough, Aunt Un.
- Let go. This is my family.

244
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:17,640
- It's none of your business!
- Aunt Un! Aunt Un!

245
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:20,800
Pin is a human too. She has feelings.

246
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:21,760
Aunt Un!

247
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:23,359
But I'm her mother!

248
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,359
A mother has no right to harm her child.

249
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,520
Aunt Un.

250
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:28,600
Don't you feel bad for Pin at all?

251
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:32,440
All this time, Pin has had to shoulder
everyone else's messes.

252
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:35,560
And Pin has to end up marrying Mr. Yai
because of Madam herself!

253
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:39,000
You're lucky enough
that Pin hasn't been in prison

254
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:41,280
or been killed, Auntie!

255
00:17:58,080 --> 00:18:00,560
Mom. Mom…

256
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,800
Mom.

257
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:26,040
Is no one here going
to do anything at all?

258
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:27,560
I'm about to lose my patience.

259
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,880
Auntie told us to wait.

260
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,200
Just stay calm, On.

261
00:18:34,400 --> 00:18:35,760
Can you go see what's happening?

262
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,000
No way.

263
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:43,120
Didn't you see how wild it was out there?

264
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:45,120
I don't want to become a thief's woman.

265
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:50,000
Fine. I'll go see for myself.

266
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,760
Let's see if they dare lay a hand on me.

267
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:54,720
Jan, film it and show it to the police.

268
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:56,280
- Wait, Miss.
- On.

269
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:58,200
- Are we really doing that?
- Yes.

270
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:59,400
On.

271
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,680
Nothing's happening now, On.

272
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:05,560
I've talked to Mr. Yai.

273
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,520
So what did you agree on?

274
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:10,000
Is he going to give us Paisal Farm?

275
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:11,520
Or are we doing fifty-fifty?

276
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,600
If Na is the rightful heir to this place,

277
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,320
why do you still need to talk to him?

278
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,760
With a thug like him,

279
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:22,920
don't bother caring about him
or giving him any attention.

280
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,640
Just get the police here to arrest him.

281
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,520
Come here.

282
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:30,520
Sit down and talk to me.

283
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:31,840
Let's sit down.

284
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:34,400
Listen to me, okay?

285
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:37,480
Well, the police
don't really want to meddle

286
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:39,240
in a family matter.

287
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,200
It's no use reporting him.

288
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:45,320
Let's just do it my way,
and everything will end nicely.

289
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,640
I promise.

290
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,680
What do you mean by your way?

291
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:50,880
Pin is one of us.

292
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:55,080
The more Mr. Yai is infatuated with her,
the more we gain the upper hand.

293
00:19:56,920 --> 00:20:00,240
Same old technique. She always does that.

294
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:03,200
It'd be perfect if you just shut up, Nee.

295
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,920
We don't need to do anything now.

296
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:11,200
Just play along.

297
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:15,200
And Pin will do the work for us.

298
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:21,080
But if you want me to lower myself
to do a double wedding

299
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:23,480
with a maid and a criminal like that,

300
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,720
I'll pass.

301
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:30,000
I won't allow that either.

302
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:32,360
Your and Na's wedding

303
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:35,360
must be the fanciest in the province,
no matter what.

304
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,680
We won't be ashamed, I promise.

305
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:40,840
We can't just make it the fanciest.

306
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,560
It has to be tasteful too.

307
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,280
Right. Of course.

308
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,440
Auntie.

309
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:58,120
Did Pin really agree
to marry Mr. Yai for us?

310
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:03,360
No matter what her reason is,
we must benefit from her decision.

311
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:07,760
I believe she still loves you.

312
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:10,080
You have to be nice to her.

313
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:12,840
I'll have her work for us.

314
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,920
Mom.

315
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:34,040
I'm going to the wedding now.

316
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:39,120
I'll have Noi come pick you up.

317
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,080
Jin?

318
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:06,280
How did you get here?

319
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:10,200
Pan called
and asked me to be your bridesmaid,

320
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:13,520
so I rushed here to help you
in case you needed anything.

321
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:15,920
Thank you so much.

322
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:23,240
So, what dress are you supposed to wear?

323
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:25,400
Who's doing your hair and makeup?

324
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,920
No one told me anything.

325
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:30,120
Mr. Yai told me to wait here.

326
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,960
But forget about it.

327
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,600
I'll just wear this dress.

328
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:36,040
There won't be so many guests.

329
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,960
Uh, is it time?

330
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:52,680
Not yet. I brought stylists for you two.

331
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:05,160
Dress up the bride and everyone.

332
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,400
You have two hours.

333
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,520
- Got it.
- Got it.

334
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:19,800
Hey.

335
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,640
What's with that outfit?

336
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,720
These are brand-name pajamas, Na.

337
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,800
Manager Pan asked
for everyone to gather downstairs.

338
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:33,640
Well, ever since you switched sides,

339
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:36,120
you've been so well-dressed, Win.

340
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:40,080
There are a lot of guests today. Mr. Yai
doesn't want our farm to disappoint.

341
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:43,000
So, are you still not dressed and ready,
Madam, Ms. Nee?

342
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:46,120
I thought I'd just go down for a second
then come back up to sleep.

343
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:50,040
The wedding must be
full of stinky farmhands or filthy thugs.

344
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:51,560
I won't be able to tolerate them.

345
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:56,560
At first, I thought about wearing
a sarong and a grandma lace-trimmed top,

346
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,760
but it wouldn't suit someone of our class.

347
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,560
Or should we go with this look?

348
00:24:00,640 --> 00:24:04,080
Flip-flops, powdered faces,
gold jewelry, and sky-high hair?

349
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,760
So adorable.

350
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:32,440
Why are there so many guests?

351
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:33,680
Foreigners too?

352
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:35,520
Right? I'm so confused.

353
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:37,720
The province's
most prominent figures are all here

354
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:39,440
I had to rush back to put my suit on.

355
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:43,000
Auntie, should we go get changed?

356
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:46,240
Oh, the bride's family.

357
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:47,560
There you are.

358
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:53,840
Wow, spending this much for the wedding,

359
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:56,200
I guess a lot of the stolen money
is already gone.

360
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,880
This is Mr. Yai, Chalit,

361
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:00,440
the adoptive nephew of Pload
of Padang Besar, starting his family life.

362
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:01,920
How could we do it smaller?

363
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:06,720
For today, Mr. Yai has also invited
the guests staying at the resort

364
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:09,080
and Pin's friends
to come celebrate as well.

365
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:12,520
And most importantly,
your guests were invited as well.

366
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:15,360
Madam Krongsuk!

367
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:16,760
There they are.

368
00:25:17,360 --> 00:25:19,080
Madam Kanittha?

369
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:21,880
What… What brings you here?

370
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:25,840
Your stepson is getting married,
and you didn't tell us anything.

371
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:28,160
It was very sudden.

372
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,760
So, how did you find out?

373
00:25:31,360 --> 00:25:33,960
Your stepson had someone call and tell us.

374
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:35,920
See? We're all here.

375
00:25:37,080 --> 00:25:39,000
Your dress looks rather plain today.

376
00:25:39,080 --> 00:25:40,400
It's not like you at all.

377
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:42,720
We went all out with our diamonds

378
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:43,920
because we didn't want to be outshone.

379
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,680
Yes. Look at us.

380
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:49,800
Well, the tailor couldn't make
my dress in time.

381
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:53,040
And for the diamond jewelry at the bank,

382
00:25:53,120 --> 00:25:54,760
I couldn't retrieve it in time either.

383
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:57,000
That's a relief.

384
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:59,080
I thought you had pawned it all
at the gambling den,

385
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:02,440
since you haven't paid
my loan's interest at all.

386
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,560
Well, this is an auspicious occasion.

387
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:10,280
Should we stop talking
about unfortunate topics?

388
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:13,280
Oh, right, I forgot. Please forgive me.

389
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,880
I'll go take a seat.

390
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:19,040
Hold on. Wait for me.

391
00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:21,240
Excuse me.
I need to go welcome other guests.

392
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,360
Madam.

393
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,800
Where are you going?

394
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,280
Go serve the drinks to the guests.

395
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:31,360
I'm not your servant.

396
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:34,320
With your completely out-of-place outfit,

397
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,760
you're lucky
I don't have you do the dishes.

398
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:41,120
Or do I need a gun to make you listen?

399
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:53,720
This one, please.

400
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:55,960
- Where did Jom go?
- This one.

401
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,880
I haven't seen him since last night.

402
00:26:57,960 --> 00:27:01,200
And he didn't show up
when we were prepping the venue either.

403
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,720
Yai turned off his phone,
and I couldn't reach Dad either.

404
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,080
What is he up to now?

405
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:25,560
This is so strange.

406
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:27,960
Even now,
no one has shown up to take us there.

407
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,400
And we can't get in touch with anyone.

408
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:32,120
It has almost passed the auspicious time.

409
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:34,680
Pin.

410
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:37,360
Don't you feel troubled at all?

411
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,960
Mr. Yai might be playing a trick on you.

412
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,040
Just let it be.

413
00:27:42,120 --> 00:27:44,560
Whatever happens, happens, Jin.

414
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:49,040
What was that noise?

415
00:27:49,120 --> 00:27:50,160
Gunshots?

416
00:27:52,120 --> 00:27:55,080
Hey, Pin. Pin, wait for me.

417
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:23,080
Still clumsy as ever, Puny Pin.

418
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:16,720
Why hasn't the ceremony started yet?

419
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,240
It's late, Madam.

420
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:31,120
Krong, I heard someone outside
say that Yai is nowhere to be found.

421
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:34,880
Maybe he was in a car accident
or someone ordered a hit on him

422
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:36,240
and he's dead.

423
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:40,880
On texted me. I'll go see her.

424
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:41,840
Hey.

425
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,400
Let's go together.

426
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:48,200
Madam, I'm so sorry.

427
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:51,160
I'm afraid you've wasted your time
coming here.

428
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:53,600
Because now,
the playboy groom has run away,

429
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:55,600
and no one can contact him.

430
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:58,040
Please feel free to leave.

431
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:00,280
- What is this?
- How?

432
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,760
The bride and groom are here!

433
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:12,160
- Here. Wow, you're here for the food, huh?
- Thanks.

434
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,720
Who's that?

435
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:35,640
Hey, what's with you?

436
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,760
Look, look. There.

437
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:52,360
Is that a man or a solvent?

438
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,520
Pin, who's that walking with you?

439
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:17,760
He's so handsome.

440
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:23,320
I think he looks familiar. Don't tell me…

441
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,360
Mr. Yai.

442
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:31,000
- Mr. Yai?!
- Mr. Yai?!

443
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:40,680
Our honored guests,
we apologize for the delay.

444
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:43,440
Due to an unforeseen circumstance,
the groom arrived late.

445
00:31:43,520 --> 00:31:46,080
Now, without further ado,

446
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:48,400
please welcome Mr. Yai, Chalit,

447
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,600
the only heir to Paisal Farm,

448
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:54,680
and Pinanong, the beautiful bride.

449
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:03,040
Jin, Jin. Is that really Mr. Yai?

450
00:32:05,280 --> 00:32:06,880
I'm surprised too.

451
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,640
It's like he shed an outer shell.

452
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,360
Took you long enough.

453
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:15,040
So you were getting a makeover, huh?

454
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:17,160
How could I not?

455
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:18,680
My bride is this beautiful.

456
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:19,760
I had to match her, right?

457
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:23,400
Please forgive me for being late.

458
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:25,360
It took some time to work on a new look.

459
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:32,320
He speaks English too.

460
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:41,560
You're full of surprises,
aren't you, Mr. Yai?

461
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:45,640
There has to be something to keep you
on your toes, or it'd be too bland.

462
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:56,040
What's up, bro? Are you speechless?

463
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:57,840
Careful, a fly might fly into your mouth.

464
00:33:02,520 --> 00:33:03,480
You're so gorgeous, Pin.

465
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:06,120
I really didn't see this coming.

466
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:15,080
So where's your girlfriend?

467
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,720
Why don't we see who's more beautiful?

468
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:22,760
On is not feeling very well.

469
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:27,680
Let's start the ceremony, Mr. Yai.

470
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:28,960
The guests have been waiting.

471
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:33,320
Of course. I can't wait either.

472
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:39,160
Show your beautiful smile.

473
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:42,280
I sacrificed my most beloved hair
and beard for this

474
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:44,000
as your gift, you know.

475
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:49,240
Na, is that really Mr. Yai?

476
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,640
How is that possible?

477
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:53,400
A thief suddenly turned into an angel.

478
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:57,800
I want him. I want him, Na.

479
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,920
Hey.

480
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:00,880
Tawin.

481
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,160
Thank you so much

482
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:08,240
for taking care
of everything on this side for Mr. Yai.

483
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:11,320
Thank you as well

484
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:14,400
for looking after Mr. Paisal's son
until this day.

485
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:45,240
Mr. Yai, it's time
to put the ring on the bride's finger.

486
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:20,840
Groom, please give the bride
a kiss on the cheek.

487
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:24,720
Okay.

488
00:37:34,120 --> 00:37:35,200
Oh, my.

489
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:58,640
CHALIT

490
00:38:13,720 --> 00:38:16,600
PINANONG

491
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,320
MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE

492
00:38:51,240 --> 00:38:53,400
Pin is like my daughter.

493
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,960
I raised her myself.

494
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:58,840
I promise that she'll do a great job
taking care of you,

495
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:01,440
just like how I cared for Mr. Paisal.

496
00:39:03,160 --> 00:39:04,960
I'm not weak like my dad was.

497
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:06,560
You don't need to worry about me.

498
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:18,120
Congratulations, Pin.

499
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:20,600
I never imagined I'd see this day.

500
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,080
I'm so glad

501
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:25,080
I brought you and your mother along
to this place.

502
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:28,560
You never fail to give me what I want.

503
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:37,480
Don't forget what we agreed.

504
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:21,360
Who are you looking for?

505
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,920
Your sweetheart is sitting right there.

506
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,640
Don't always assume the worst.

507
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,080
I'm looking for Mom.

508
00:40:29,680 --> 00:40:31,440
I want her to give us blessings.

509
00:40:48,080 --> 00:40:49,240
Pin's waiting for you, Aunt Un.

510
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,680
She really wants your blessings.

511
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,400
Aunt Un?

512
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,440
Aunt Un?

513
00:41:18,160 --> 00:41:19,120
Mom!

514
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:20,040
Mr. Yai.

515
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:21,960
- Mom.
- Yai.

516
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,320
Let go of me!

517
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:52,400
We're lucky I saw her first,
or it would have been a big mess.

518
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:54,320
What the hell are you doing?

519
00:41:55,120 --> 00:41:56,200
Madam.

520
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:57,920
I'm going to kill Yai.

521
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:00,040
If he dies, all our problems will end.

522
00:42:00,120 --> 00:42:01,760
I'll go to prison myself.

523
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:04,800
Do you really think he's going
to let you kill him that easily?

524
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:08,400
And if he doesn't die,
you and your daughter will be in trouble.

525
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:11,760
But you were the one who told me to do it.

526
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,960
I said it because I was mad.

527
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:18,320
Un, I already know

528
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:21,480
that you truly care about me.

529
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:23,960
But you need to stay calm.

530
00:42:24,040 --> 00:42:25,560
We still have other ways.

531
00:42:27,320 --> 00:42:30,000
What ways, Madam? I can't see any at all.

532
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:33,080
Uh, if you see

533
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:36,080
how the wedding is being held,

534
00:42:36,680 --> 00:42:41,120
you'll realize that
Yai is really infatuated with Pin.

535
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:44,680
He even brought the officers here
to register the marriage certificate.

536
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:47,600
He wants Pin as his legitimate wife.

537
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:51,280
But he is still a vile criminal.

538
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:57,320
As long as he has money,
the law can't do anything to him, Aunt Un.

539
00:42:59,560 --> 00:43:02,400
And we're just going
to let him pick on us like this?

540
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:07,000
Right now, we're at a disadvantage.

541
00:43:08,120 --> 00:43:10,680
Only Pin can help us.

542
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:17,440
Congratulations, Mr. Yai.

543
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:22,120
I hope you succeed in building the family

544
00:43:22,640 --> 00:43:24,640
you've always dreamed of.

545
00:43:26,520 --> 00:43:27,960
No matter how hard it is,

546
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:30,640
I'll be there to help you.

547
00:43:38,640 --> 00:43:40,000
Congratulations, Pinanong.

548
00:43:45,880 --> 00:43:47,200
A good wife

549
00:43:48,360 --> 00:43:51,280
is the driving force behind her family's

550
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,200
and her husband's success,

551
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:55,040
not the one who brings disaster.

552
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:58,000
I hope

553
00:43:59,240 --> 00:44:01,200
you can be a good wife for Mr. Yai.

554
00:44:31,400 --> 00:44:33,040
I'm starting to wonder

555
00:44:33,120 --> 00:44:35,040
if your aunt is hiding something.

556
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:37,320
Mr. Yai marrying Pinanong

557
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:39,640
is like keeping
a venomous snake by his side.

558
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:42,560
If you're sure
you're not going to betray Madam,

559
00:44:42,640 --> 00:44:43,560
you have to prove it.

560
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:45,720
Give all your dowry to me.

561
00:44:45,800 --> 00:44:47,960
The security camera you had me install

562
00:44:48,040 --> 00:44:49,440
really wasn't a waste.

563
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:38,000
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
